resources.string: Are you a Member of IEEE Committee

We are a team that is continuously trying to develop and create opportunities for growth and learning aligned with our objectives. Our success is achieved through dedication in thought, word and action, and our ethical conduct and sincerity of purpose, through our student branch, make us proud to be part of IEEE.

• IEEE membership offers access to technical innovation, networking opportunities, and exclusive member benefits.
• Build a platform to introduce careers in technology to students around the world.
• Access to research, news, educational resources to expand expertise and stay current.
• Get access to competitions, scholarships, awards, educational courses, certifications and conferences.
